cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use OpenGATE in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "OpenGATE: Open Grounded AI Testing & Evaluation"
abstract: >-
  An open-source framework for evaluating evidence-grounded AI systems.
  Deterministic scorers, hand-labelled gold sets, and a CI regression gate
  measure whether a system can prove its answers from source material —
  across evidence QA, redaction, simplification, retrieval, and grounding
  capabilities.
authors:
